<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.8">
<l>vēyka ḷōṅki veṇmut tutira veṭikoḷ cuṭalaiyu</l>
<l>ḷoyu muruvi lulaṟu kūnta lalaṟu pakuvāya</l>
<l>pēykaḷ kūṭip piṇaṅkaṇ mānti yaṇaṅkum peruṅkāṭṭil</l>
<l>māya ṉāṭa malaiyāṉ makaḷu maruṇṭu nōkkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While white pearls drop as the bamboos become high, on the crackling pyre,</l>
<l>in the big cremation ground where demonesses -- [their] mouths split in crying,</l>
<l>withered tresses, in tired forms -- gather [and] eat [and] worry corpses,</l>
<l>while the mysterious one dances the daughter of Him from the mountain looks on in confusion.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
